      <section>
         <title>Uninstallation</title>
         <ul>
            <li>Open the <strong>Control Panel</strong> <br /> <img alt="Windows Control Panel"
            src="images/PC_18_control_panel_addremove.png" /></li>
            <li>Press <strong>Add or remove programs</strong></li>
            <li>Browse down to <strong>Sámi Proofing Tools</strong> and click the item <br /> <img
            alt="Sami Proofing tools are marked" src="images/PC_19_remove_sami_proofing_tools.png" /></li>
            <li>Click the <strong>Remove</strong> button.</li>
            <li>When the removal process is finished, the <strong>Sámi Proofing Tools</strong> item in the list of
            installed programs will have disappeared</li>
            <li>If you have the South Sámi beta installed and want to remove it, select
            <strong>SouthSamiSpellerBeta1</strong> and click <strong>Change/Remove</strong>:<br /><img alt="???"
            src="images/PC_20_remove_sma_beta.png" /></li>
         </ul>
      </section>
